      "date": "2011-05-26 09:21:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIf this is being pushed to master then it needs to have an LU-xxx JIRA ticket. This is for 2 reasons;\n\nMost importantly the JIRA LU-xxx project needs to be the definitive tracker of changes made to Lustre.\n\nSecondly other projects are not always public and so if we don't always post to LU many changes will take place behind closed doors.",
